{"title":"Deficit B12","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Bioestadística/Paper. Deficit B12-2025-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"DEFICIENCIA DE\\NVITAMINA B12","guid":"zLxaggbmkfQuVZFEgvyMqg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"## El Problema Clínico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- Deficiencia de vitamina B12 → causa reversible de fallo de médula ósea y enfermedad desmielinizante del sistema nervioso","guid":"yr8JFcARJV_KnDH0EYOQYQ","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"- Vitamina B12\\N(cobalamina)","guid":"NVRT98MtpRE1ut_wLav1jw","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"- Sintetizada por microorganismos","guid":"cpeUGTLhCPaxj0a4E70iRA","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"3","text":"- Detectada principalmente en alimentos de origen animal","guid":"1FIADSzLVp-g24qwxfZvIg","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"3","text":"- Absorción en el tracto\\Ngastrointestinal depende de:","guid":"M52fugEFpBUJ3WLF8y5mbA","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"- Factor intrínseco (sintetizado por células parietales gástricas)","guid":"fwC4malInGdOfaKdQz_F5g","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"- Receptor \"cubam\" en íleon distal","guid":"e_e-gVlaq2bltotOmd1Uuw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"- Causa más frecuente de deficiencia severa: pérdida de factor intrínseco por gastritis atrófica autoinmune (\"anemia perniciosa\")","guid":"J9u68T3uLtaiJ5jEQ0WT3A","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"0","text":"## Fisiopatología de la\\NDeficiencia de Vitamina B12","guid":"","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"- Cofactor para solo\\Ndos enzimas:","guid":"WKey_2faXPT-1HTfwsld-w","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"- Metionina sintasa","guid":"-MbtJM3bwji6GHiGnqQDpw","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"- L-metilmalonil-coenzima A mutasa","guid":"YKi3WE6re241xzs49UxNUw","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"10","text":"- Inter