,"parent":"0","text":"## Causas de Deficiencia\\Nde Vitamina B12","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"- Malabsorción\\Nsevera:","guid":"IG63uHWPqWBzjnKvx7PI5Q","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"- Anemia perniciosa (gastritis autoinmune)","guid":"hUi0YW0fyIANkT5OOczW7g","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"- Gastrectomía total o parcial","guid":"vPdxaN9SDZM_5AoHH5-O-Q","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"30","text":"- Cirugía de bypass gástrico u otras cirugías bariátricas","guid":"Nl9elaySv6xkiv93Lf8Z6A","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"30","text":"- Resección ileal","guid":"-gefHQp56QHIuwEUP3OtTg","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"30","text":"- Enfermedad inflamatoria intestinal","guid":"oeZPMVgOKmMh7ro2flH6TA","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"30","text":"- Síndrome de Imerslund-Gräsbeck","guid":"YEcYl1-cl4wSaApM-E5Ztg","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"29","text":"- Malabsorción\\Nleve:","guid":"81mvBJCPx9if2VZ2oacRog","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"- Malabsorción de vitamina B12 unida a proteínas","guid":"eC7LMbeBvvuE6JccY559XQ","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"- Gastritis atrófica leve","guid":"zTS8UFTpWjSp_QNvcajSJw","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"- Uso de metformina","guid":"uZD5B6ztAEoOvw_xdu9s1Q","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"37","text":"- Uso de medicamentos que bloquean ácido estomacal","guid":"8ENFRzxieZoZZDA-QfHgeg","children":[]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"29","text":"- Deficiencia\\Ndietética:","guid":"rx6IROIOdGILPCYuTVzlbw","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"- Dieta vegana o vegetariana","guid":"wx1l79i2PYbDI5_QjK1piw","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"- Lactancia materna (madres con deficiencia de B12)","guid":"7EiUHRYimBwON_GS_OFqvQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"0","text":"## Evaluación y Diagnóstico","guid":"2Hmzr_t1nY-7sOBSn8OYsA","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"- Historia clínica:","guid":"njZmjdmEJyuR3zdzyuN1dQ","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"- Síntomas de anemia","guid":"BWDnX93lLHSQPH0h14V4xQ","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"- Trastornos subyacentes que causan malabsorción","guid":"f0eFuq0Gf6psPle_wQkxjA","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"- Síntomas neurológicos (parestesias simétricas, problemas de marcha)","guid":"Tx3-nzp6B8zPKoTxs1V2Cw","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"45","text":"- Examen físico:","guid":"h_mGe2kWCvMu9Ttgo9urWA","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"- Palidez, edema, cambios pigmentarios en piel, ictericia","guid":"_K62CMFLDGpHPpW-sJ5Ffg","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"- Defectos neurológicos (sensibilidad vibratoria alterada, ataxia, debilidad)","guid":"0X4TxNaADpn1leGJooT5GA","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"45","text":"- Pruebas\\Ndiagnósticas:","guid":"-So-ahBRebJT2pE36TsFfw","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"- Nivel sérico de vitamina B12 (<200 pg/ml sugiere deficiencia)","guid":"qCNe5uIcYAJqPi7KYAYQ7g","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"- Alta tasa de falsos positivos y negativos","guid":"WLD2boRx-uzd9JjUDasEew","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"53","text":"- Ácido metilmalónico sérico (>400 nmol/L)","guid":"xoTB57w_U5rC0qfHDaiQEA","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"- 98% sensibilidad para deficiencia clínica","guid":"XXFuUQ4PzdHaSHNtT9rwiA","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"53","text":"- Homocisteína total sérica (>21 μmol/L)","guid":"r3LtxszoZ2WwDz1WXR_O2w","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"- 96% sensibilidad para deficiencia clínica","guid":"nD_kl8xctQsOTfmh8THanw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"45","text":"- Pruebas para\\Ndeterminar causa:","guid":"6YylbvROXDlVoAxsjpMp0w","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"- Anticuerpos anti-factor intrínseco (50% sensibilidad, 100% especificidad)","guid":"MZq42waWywJERmQHnQBPIQ","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"- Anticuerpos anti-células parietales (80% sensibilidad, 50-100% especificidad)","guid":"Le4WLe7A353dz17lrZLmmA","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"- Gastrina sérica en ayunas elevada (>100 pmol/L)","guid":"Nm0Gg6Wu423itTak6a3mDQ","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"- Pepsinógeno I sérico bajo (<30 μg/L)","guid":"joFQsETG4jTQBnx0Qy4Rog","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"0","text":"# HALLAZGOS HEMATOLÓGICOS EN\\NDEFICIENCIA DE VITAMINA B12","guid":"vG-8urS6bforHUEcaXUQSQ","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"## Sangre Periférica\\N(Panel A)","guid":"DP1bvGigs1ob7S2dqvcEKw","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"- Macrocitos ovales","guid":"PfCkz9E6Vmbc9U8xbbjLoA","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"- Células fragmentadas y deformadas","guid":"aGYScQSeFngCpObWP0ARHA","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"66","text":"- Célula roja nucleada megaloblástica inmadura\\N(señalada con flecha)","guid":"mg4qCXguYqWj8dNtwuNDsQ","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"66","text":"- Variación en tamaño\\Ny forma de eritrocitos","guid":"tW1YbZidugyXcCsAemY18Q","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"- Puede confundirse con anemia hemolítica microangiopática","guid":"dQCbHLiW1znBc9ylCGM7FQ","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"- Volumen corpuscular medio en rango normal","guid":"_Ad5aEHJZ2ub7aYTI6rvWw","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"- Índice de distribución de glóbulos rojos extremadamente elevado","guid":"w3hHLFWv0FhDz4CPA7ozhA","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"70","text":"- Macrocitosis combinada con células microcíticas fragmentadas","guid":"Uqnc2uqwmnsnutsntpGaUA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"65","text":"## Médula\\NÓsea (Panel B)","guid":"odAwk6a0EJb3cUWmYP6rNQ","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"- Características megaloblásticas","guid":"k9AHWQyYoxwitr6yB6B5Kg","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"- Eritroblastos grandes y precursores eritroides","guid":"ucQHf4Yi5GelYkvLlsUsNw","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"- Patrón de cromatina nuclear abierto e inmaduro","guid":"R69rMj3zrQhrdwHkWBW4_Q","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"75","text":"- Desincronía entre maduración\\Nde citoplasma y núcleos","guid":"qAWtYVNfZddUBqLGcw6UIg","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"- Afecta a precursores eritroides\\Ntardíos y granulocíticos","guid":"2vZ8Y87cTs-ty_u840a0Xg","children":[]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"75","text":"- Presencia de banda \"gigante\"","guid":"Hn5SAZ71Ge1_fxvWNLcKKA","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"75","text":"- Precursores eritroides con núcleos displásicos (flechas)","guid":"orZfBZas2LKMtsDhQJ4I0w","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"75","text":"- Fragmentos nucleares\\N(punta de flecha)","guid":"nZV4d2JQJlfZqjuzfomQZw","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"- Compatibles con apoptosis celular","guid":"ui3LRBQdUfEgq_7R1dub7w","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"- Asociados a hemólisis intramedular","guid":"s5vlMPy1fzjA7VfLMKCmKQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"0","text":"## Tratamiento","guid":"MMJPuzKlqAtvGk9L-TRPuQ","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"- Requerimiento diario: 2.4 μg","guid":"AYqVAGnFCiPPyL9-QMMRtw","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"- Suplementación\\Nparenteral:","guid":"wLzYLT29ACEEOhnNJQo3tQ","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"- Cianocobalamina 1000 μg intramuscular","guid":"yvM9NlUN7dtpWBMmwrf8YA","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"- Esquema: diario/días alternos por 1 semana → semanal por 4-8 semanas → mensual de por vida","guid":"A0K1jWfvErhOdH7NWmOqGA","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"86","text":"- Suplementación\\Noral de alta dosis:","guid":"dogNzR9HfBf59fUcDxxWOw","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"- Tabletas de 1000-2000 μg diarios","guid":"CYQ8nMk6XOEDRiIUXQ9o8w","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"- Tan efectiva como inyecciones intramusculares","guid":"lr8PD7hirpHLDowEqM-b4g","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"- 0.5-4% de la vitamina B12 oral se absorbe por difusión pasiva","guid":"OQVW4ck5b-w3kCns2hUIYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"86","text":"- Respuesta al\\Ntratamiento:","guid":"blQ-bdXk6UxQmEDMppezuA","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"- Respuesta hematológica rápida (aumento de reticulocitos en 1 semana)","guid":"LvFzHcmqSYmKOohhHSCDqA","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"- Corrección de anemia megaloblástica en 6-8 semanas","guid":"zwV4dBA9_K23DFHsDLIcDw","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"- Síntomas neurológicos pueden empeorar transitoriamente antes de mejorar","guid":"kGrVrAuomWQV4nR9R0yH2Q","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"95","text":"- La recuperación neurológica depende de la gravedad y duración de las anormalidades","guid":"8sNf2Dng0s6APiUqsDRcSQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"0","text":"# CAUSAS, TRATAMIENTO Y\\NSEGUIMIENTO DE LA\\NDEFICIENCIA DE VITAMINA B12","guid":"NqW8U_1rq18ukHbm2kY20g","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"## I. Malabsorción Severa","guid":"SyuahCXk7yar9Z7a2gtvMg","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"- **Anemia perniciosa\\N(gastritis autoinmune)**","guid":"RJO_Oo-JJ-3G27MFA79fCQ","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"- Tratamiento: Cianocobalamina 1000 μg IM diario/días\\Nalternos × 1 semana → semanal × 4-8 semanas →\\Nmensual de por vida, o cianocobalamina oral\\N1000-2000 μg diario de por vida","guid":"jBWcbe2tG3hwyTFPa_2ncQ","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"- Seguimiento: Suplementar hierro y folato según necesidad;\\Nvigilar otras condiciones autoinmunes (especialmente\\Ntiroideas); endoscopia en pacientes con síntomas de cáncer\\Ngástrico o deficiencia de hierro","guid":"4MWPLKoZmBWI4fa3Uh_AgA","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"101","text":"- **Otras causas de\\Nmalabsorción severa:**","guid":"PmNejFqz4ZOBwgf9WBcOtg","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"- Gastrectomía\\Ntotal o parcial","guid":"Zq0IwFBaVCppSUMAtNw6vw","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"- Bypass gástrico u otras\\Ncirugías bariátricas","guid":"6G1Z10D9NHCXf3yw8Rx04w","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"- Resección ileal o\\Ncirugía reconstructiva","guid":"uMT787GYBN4b1y7oegqE6g","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"105","text":"- Enfermedad inflamatoria\\Nintestinal, esprue tropical","guid":"mK7LSMcsob-hLJuttWxECw","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"105","text":"- Síndrome de\\NImerslund-Gräsbeck","guid":"sIx_gc4kQ9Wvc8a3WM6t0Q","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"105","text":"- Tratamiento: Igual que\\Nanemia perniciosa","guid":"Qm8E40C9gtbPGCViVy-wmw","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"105","text":"- Seguimiento: Similar a anemia\\Nperniciosa; asesoramiento genético\\Nen síndromes hereditarios","guid":"Ca61jR4XeN12-WS51pymSA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"100","text":"## II. Malabsorción Leve","guid":"q18KqMS6ChEs5TnheD9vug","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"- **Malabsorción de vitamina\\NB12 unida a proteínas**","guid":"0Bg_hVauWmfKQz2IwHrqVw","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"- Tratamiento: Cianocobalamina oral 500-1000 μg diario o IM\\N1000 μg diario/días alternos × 1 semana → semanal × 4-8\\Nsemanas → mensual de por vida","guid":"aSvsYLVtqlDDKDcKW9Exhg","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"114","text":"- Seguimiento: Evaluar deficiencia de hierro,\\Nanemia por enfermedad renal crónica y\\Nanemia por inflamación crónica","guid":"K1tYQDih-KVlQCbzxcX1kg","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"113","text":"- **Otras causas de\\Nmalabsorción leve:**","guid":"_6ZnBXtwEi4_j_dOmxn9gg","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"- Gastritis atrófica leve","guid":"5tgNwbrK_zjpnLf3OWWJ3A","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"- Uso de metformina","guid":"07cU67FiybMmTOO8qGrY8w","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"117","text":"- Uso de medicamentos que\\Nbloquean ácido estomacal","guid":"ZS3kLtsSWhghx_9uDfft9Q","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"117","text":"- Tratamiento y seguimiento:\\NIgual que malabsorción de B12\\Nunida a proteínas","guid":"EVFHs3l6H12pfsVejWz5tw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"100","text":"## III.\\NDeficiencia\\NDietética","guid":"ZfSV4wRdn5odFFd0AMpQ1g","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"- **Adultos: Dieta vegana/vegetariana\\No baja en carne y lácteos**","guid":"E3S3E4Wn02GsAfVcZA_Q2A","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"- Tratamiento: Suplementos\\Ncon >2 μg de vitamina B12 o\\Nalimentos fortificados","guid":"wMkkXtncqNoHhekt59QJOQ","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"123","text":"- Seguimiento: Evaluar deficiencia\\Nde hierro (muy común)","guid":"om2KpueVGwYOn_TAiQvMnQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"122","text":"- **Infantes: Lactancia materna con\\Nmadres deficientes en B12**","guid":"uxRN8SZqmenqbKNkprIqmA","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"- Tratamiento: Cianocobalamina IM 250-1000 μg diario\\N→ semanal hasta recuperación; tratamiento de la\\Nmadre; suplementación oral con 1-2 μg diarios o\\Nfórmula/alimentos enriquecidos","guid":"hYUPKZkuc3nLI49-EZFAQg","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"- Seguimiento: Confirmar respuesta metabólica en\\Ninfantes o derivar a especialista en genética;\\Nconsejería nutricional para madres","guid":"1QjhzRbWkllJgmOTCEnaTw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"100","text":"## IV. Casos Especiales","guid":"Ily7OU8XmMBXK_x0m1NH9Q","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"- **Niños:**","guid":"SNgZd3MQUzal2YSp58dKkg","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"- Enfermedades\\Nsimilares a adultos","guid":"9Ylf_5KY2zQaN1jFTKaT2Q","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"130","text":"- Tratamiento: 100 μg IM mensual o dosis\\Noral alta diaria (según edad)","guid":"YW8ICqjXLVVNhMbpnxfF5A","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"130","text":"- Seguimiento: Confirmar anemia\\Nperniciosa o malabsorción congénita","guid":"liyhmE-6atVqYE8qDB-gqA","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"129","text":"- **Óxido nitroso:**","guid":"jKE41WdsCwqU_7fP5dr1pw","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"- Abuso recreativo/ocupacional o\\Nanestesia en perniciosa oculta","guid":"R6EsNVZsLgkDb5GOuIMVJA","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"- Tratamiento: Cianocobalamina\\N1000 μg IM (igual esquema que\\Nanemia perniciosa)","guid":"cwfZ-f9AdF-YmUZcdYLfWQ","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"- Seguimiento: Evaluar malabsorción de\\NB12; consejería para adicciones","guid":"QSQihAqpQAeZ9uIqM874jw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"100","text":"## Notas Importantes","guid":"mJCRxBmT4PUVp0wQXKAlMw","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"- La hidroxocobalamina IM puede sustituir a cianocobalamina (documentar respuesta a intervalos de 3 meses)","guid":"Y7QUcT2Z98plBwx_cVRDzw","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"- El óxido nitroso inactiva la enzima metionina sintasa dependiente de B12 y causa formación de análogos de B12","guid":"EaKnynLMmSyTVtt0LAl7dA","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"138","text":"- Las malabsorciones congénitas resultan de mutaciones del receptor ileal cubam, cubilina o amnionless","guid":"ULLlzSJlV98UJONTzuKMnA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"0","text":"##\\NConsideraciones\\NEspeciales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"- Deficiencia\\Nen infantes:","guid":"PvTJyDwQasHZWtc5z1b4Fg","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"- Manifestaciones: retraso en desarrollo cerebral y general, regresión,\\Nhipotonía, dificultades alimentarias, letargia, hiperirritabilidad","guid":"J6uPqOZNiGSzQwduYRvxRA","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"- Tratamiento: reemplazo rápido para prevenir discapacidades permanentes","guid":"gHh-jyxHgxBruSUoDg4i8Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"146","parent":"142","text":"- Anemia\\Nperniciosa:","guid":"EIY2Tdz8qx3KHeAZHuKw6g","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"- Requiere tratamiento de por vida","guid":"IEXfHdlvyiqqxWFdh6mBpg","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"- Mayor asociación con otras enfermedades autoinmunes (tiroideas, diabetes tipo 1, vitíligo)","guid":"eqTXYkTM90cPAIBEejWXgA","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"146","text":"- Vigilancia para detección de cáncer gástrico","guid":"HSjLjN03S8QXm6IUxkFEJw","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":149,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Bioestadística","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Bioestadística","filename":"Paper. Deficit B12-2025-1","id":"map_196","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Paper. Deficit B12-2025-1"}